'''Chitima''' (Train in English) ingoro ine injini inofamba panjanji dzakagadzirwa nesimbi. Injini ndiyo ine simba rokusairira chitima kuti chifambe; iyo injini inenge ichisairira ngoro dzinotakura vanhu kana nhumbi. Kune mhando dzezvitima zvinoshanda nediesel, coal, uye magetsi.

